{"word":"ἐναυλίζω","slug":"ἐναυλίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐναυλίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to dwell</i> or <i>abide in</i> aplace, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>ἐναυλίζομαι</el> <i>to take up one's quarters in</i> a place during night, <i>to take up nightquarters, bivouac</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}